    Enumeration containing the protocol names for IF-T protocol bindings.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      PEAP1
      TCG IF-T binding for Tunneled EAP Methods using Protected EAP version 1.0.
      PEAP1_1
      TCG IF-T binding for Tunneled EAP Methods using Protected EAP version 1.1.
      PLAIN1
      HSB IF-T binding for testing purpose using no encryption only version is version 1.0.
      TEAP1
      TCG IF-T binding for Tunneled EAP Methods version 1.0.
      TEAP1_1
      TCG IF-T binding for Tunneled EAP Methods version 1.1.
      TLS1
      TCG binding to TLS version 2.0 aliased by IETF to 1.0.
